// masters_messages.go — hand-written proto message types for master data CRUD RPCs.
//
// Covers: Hotel, Airline, Muthawwif, Addon, DeparturePricing and all
// Request/Response wrapper types for the Wave-1A master data endpoints.
//
// NOTE: These types would normally be generated by protoc into catalog.pb.go.
// They are written by hand here because protoc is not available in the current
// environment. Run `make genpb` to regenerate once protoc is set up, then
// delete this file.
//
// Getters follow the protoc-gen-go pattern so handler code compiles unchanged
// once regenerated.

package pb

